subSection.paragraph:
In addition to the published literature (Miedema 1978; 
Vierbergen & Loomans 2009
; 
Siepel et al. 2018
) we have found 9 additional species new for the fauna of 
The Netherlands
in our projects’ samplings as well as in our personal collection. This paper aims to re-describe them as well as 4 other species based on the collected specimens.

